Discussion in 'Albums (lossless)' started by Eric Lyn, 2 minutes ago.

    Cosmic is the 11th (labeled as ninth) mini album by Red Velvet. It was released on June 24, 2024 with "Cosmic" serving as the album's title track.



    Repackage version, so-called Cosmie version, which was released on August 1, 2024, includes all 6 previously released songs and one new song "Sweet Dreams" which is the title track of the album.



    Track list
    1. "Cosmic" - 3:46
    2. "Sunflower" - 3:17
    3. "Last Drop" - 3:23
    4. "Love Arcade" - 2:57
    5. "Bubble" - 3:28
    6. "Night Drive" - 3:20
    7. "Sweet Dreams" (Cosmie ver.) - 3:09
